query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('10.04',
'12.10',
'apache2',
'firefox',
'kernel',
'kubuntu',
'partitioning',
'scripts',
'shortcut-keys',
'system-installation',
'updates',
'virtualbox');
